
#Plugin insertmap

##Introduction

Allows you to insert map into your pages (google maps).

##Configuration

The google key must be configured into "Site / Manage site properties"


[Maven documentation and reports](http://dev.lutece.paris.fr/plugins/plugin-insertmap/)
